snippet.title: Hello Neighbor Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Download the Pre-Alpha - http://HelloNeighborGame.com
Wishlist on Steam - http://store.steampowered.com/app/521890

Hello Neighbor is a Stealth Horror game where you sneak into your neighbor's house. You play against an advanced AI that counters your every move.

Steam - http://store.steampowered.com/app/521890
Official page - http://HelloNeighborGame.com

Powered by Unreal Engine 4.
